[h1] Code blocks

[p-]
Code blocks display text exactly as written in a monospace font inside
a dark bordered box. A copy button in the top-right corner puts the
contents on the clipboard.
[-p]

[h2] Usage

[code-]
[code-]
anything you write here
appears as-is, line by line
in a monospace font
[use -code to close (with - and no space)]
[-code]

[p-]
Everything between the opening [code-] and closing [-code] is treated
as literal text. Tags are not parsed inside a code block.
[-p]

[p] Code blocks always use the monospace font regardless of any font= set on surrounding tags.

[p] Code blocks cannot be nested.

